description:
Entitled “The Spirit Draws My Deepest Devotion,” Monday afternoon’s concert during the 61st General Conference Session welcomes listeners into a deeper relationship with God through the influence of the Holy Spirit. Musicians include:


- Advent Euphonic Chorale: Every Time I Feel the Spirit
- Daeburn Lee: The Lord’s Prayer
- Scripture Says: This Is the Way
- Siam Violin Ensemble: Jesus Wants Me for a Sunbeam
- Coral Canto Joven do Instituto Adventista Paranaense: Escolhi Seguir a Jesus (I Choose to Follow Jesus)
- 7th Element: My Faith Looks Up to Thee
- Mother’s Voice: Niwe kama Yesu (I Would Be Like Jesus)
- Eric Gonzales: Oh, I Want to Know You More
fulltitle: Music Concert "The Spirit Draws My Deepest Devotion" | Monday Afternoon
